arStrings.szText: "I found what you asked for. The lacuni were starving."

(exhales) This chitin has all the telltale signs of infection. And look here, inside. Plant matter. The very same the dregs cultivate. Dregs grow the crops, bugs eat the fruit, lacuni eat the bugs. And so the infection spreads, from kind to kind.
Damn it all. It’s too late to stop this. Far too late. All we can do is...what? Contain the spread? How?
(sighs) We must stop the attacks. The leader of this lacuni pride—find him, kill him. Everything else...everything else will have to wait.
